lyrics:
[Verse]
Time keeps ticking, it's a constant chase
Gotta find the strength to rise up in this race
Don't let failures hold you down, keep a steady pace
Motivation's the key, let it ignite your inner blaze

[Chorus]
Time to rise, shake off those doubts
Unlock the fire within, there's no time for pouts
Embrace the challenge, break through the skies
With determination, let your spirit fly high
